results.name: Expansion of e.g.f. exp(-Sum_{k>=1} x^(k^2)/k^2).
formula: E.g.f.: Product_{k>=1} (1 - x^k)^(lambda(k)/k), where lambda() is the Liouville function (A008836).
mathematica: nmax = 23; CoefficientList[Series[Exp[-Sum[x^(k^2)/k^2, {k, 1, nmax}]], {x, 0, nmax}], x] Range[0, nmax]!
nmax = 23; CoefficientList[Series[Product[(1 - x^k)^(LiouvilleLambda[k]/k), {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] Range[0, nmax]!
results.author: _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, May 24 2019
